title: Hello GD, WhyDoCatsBark is DEAD!
body:

I now go by my true form...

Best Aatrox NA!

I am so hype guys I have wanted this name since forever. The previous owner of the name has been on and off and finally went away for a long enough period. A bunch of other aatrox mains on reddit were super hype for the name to come out and I have been on all day waiting for it to unlock.

Hype.
